00:01:47.210 --> 00:01:49.130
to this stellar collection,

00:01:49.130 --> 00:01:51.490
and I'm convinced that they will have

00:01:51.490 --> 00:01:54.713
a similar impact to some of the others.

00:01:55.550 --> 00:01:59.140
The HarvEst Distinguished
Women Lecture Series

00:01:59.140 --> 00:02:01.010
