to talk about her vision

00:03:42.330 --> 00:03:44.890
in establishing this lecture series,

00:03:44.890 --> 00:03:48.670
and then I'll come and
introduce the lecturer.

00:03:48.670 --> 00:03:49.503
Esther.

00:03:51.403 --> 00:03:53.653
(applause)

