00:55:11.730 --> 00:55:15.790
He actually said that if
women didn't ask for raises,

00:55:15.790 --> 00:55:20.750
their talent would be recognized
and they would get a raise.

00:55:20.750 --> 00:55:22.130
Okay.

00:55:22.130 --> 00:55:24.553
That's a very meritocratic answer.

00:55:25.660 --> 00:55:27.790
But it turns out it flies in the face of

00:55:27.790 --> 00:55:29.660
