so all of these are averages,

00:55:38.340 --> 00:55:40.690
do not like to negotiate.

00:55:40.690 --> 00:55:45.170
Women describe negotiation
as like going to the dentist.

00:55:45.170 --> 00:55:48.710
Men describe negotiation as
like going to a ballgame.

00:55:48.710 --> 00:55:49.950
They like it.

00:55:49.950 --> 00:55:53.760
So the evidence suggests
that equally competent

00:55:53.760 --> 00:55:58.760
men and women will, the
women are much less likely

00:55:58.910 --> 00:56:01.670
to ask for a raise, much less likely.

00:56:01.670 --> 00:56:04.340
Because they don't feel good about that.

