01:14:12.210 --> 01:14:14.780
you can see that parity

01:14:14.780 --> 01:14:18.150
at the beginning is largely achieved,

01:14:18.150 --> 01:14:22.280
but it really dissipates significantly,

01:14:22.280 --> 01:14:24.360
and then the question is what's common

01:14:24.360 --> 01:14:28.470
to the companies or the countries

01:14:28.470 --> 01:14:30.410
that explains this common phenomenon.

01:14:30.410 --> 01:14:34.500
But I'm not, what would
