01:14:51.900 --> 01:14:56.700
So the very big differences in pay

01:14:56.700 --> 01:14:59.928
that result from STEM
versus non-STEM in the US

01:14:59.928 --> 01:15:03.630
may be much more extreme
than it is in Scandinavia.

01:15:03.630 --> 01:15:05.930
After all, we know in Scandinavia

01:15:05.930 --> 01:15:07.300
that teachers are paid much better

01:15:07.300 --> 01:15:08.200
than they're paid here.

01:15:08.200 --> 01:15:10.550
So just as a start you'd expect

01:15:10.550 --> 01:15:12.303
