01:16:12.950 --> 01:16:15.840
So part of this is also sectoral.

01:16:15.840 --> 01:16:18.390
So there's a lot of, what
I tried to do in the talk

01:16:18.390 --> 01:16:21.910
is sort of say that
there are common things,

01:16:21.910 --> 01:16:25.650
there are enough common
things across companies

01:16:25.650 --> 01:16:28.240
and across countries that there is

01:16:28.240 --> 01:16:30.650
a gender issue wherever you look.

01:16:30.650 --> 01:16:33.360
It manifests itself differently,

01:16:33.360 --> 01:16:35.600
but there are gender issues,

01:16:35.600 --> 01:16:39.790
both in politics and in
economic participation.

01:16:39.790 --> 01:16:41.138
That's what I would say.

