01:17:05.120 --> 01:17:06.040
before I can make the question.

01:17:06.040 --> 01:17:10.510
So Chancellor Merkel
and President Hollande

01:17:10.510 --> 01:17:14.333
recently made a trip to Moscow,
and then again to Minsk.

01:17:15.170 --> 01:17:18.570
And there was discussion,
there was a presentation

01:17:18.570 --> 01:17:21.700
by a former ambassador to
Russia, Jack Matlock, recently,

01:17:21.700 --> 01:17:23.860
at the National Press Club,

01:17:23.860 --> 01:17:26.420
that we are closer to nuclear war today

01:17:26.420 --> 01:17:29.803
than we were even in the
