studying as much as possible

01:20:08.480 --> 01:20:09.960
what's going on in the Nordic countries,

01:20:09.960 --> 01:20:11.650
and trying to do exactly the same thing.

01:20:11.650 --> 01:20:12.930
I mean, it's really quite interesting.

01:20:12.930 --> 01:20:15.823
They've adopted the Nordic
countries as their example.

01:20:17.814 --> 01:20:20.900
